title: Automobilista Legendary Tracks Part 3 Hockenheim-CODEX
description:
Automobilista.Legendary.Tracks.Part.3.Hockenheim-CODEX

Release Date: 05/2017
Protection: Steam
Discs: 1
Genre: Racing
Legendary Tracksis a line of DLCs forAutomobilista, celebrating the
heritage of classic racing circuits throughout their history. Part
3 is now here: The Hockenheimring. Host of the German GP for 35
years, the Hockenheimring is one of the tracks with richest history
in the world. Historically known for its classic layout with long
straights through the surrounding forests, the track was reformed
in time for the 2002 German GP, becoming much shorter modern
circuit but retaining a This pack features 4 distinct versions of
this legendary track from 4 different decades - 1977, 1988, 2001
and 2016, along with extra modern layouts (National, Rallycross,
Short A & B).

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/644210/
- Extract
- Burn or mount the .iso
- Run setup.exe and install
- Read .nfo
